						               													<description>Road/Kill Ultimate Car Combat is a 2-5 player table-top strategy game of fun and furious futuristic car combat that can be played in under an hour. It is the pinnacle of smash'em-up car games, loaded with sweet looking customizable high-quality minis, tons of guns&amp;rsquo;n&amp;rsquo;gear and fast-moving play tactics. This game is first-class and like nothing else on the market today.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A Streamlined Experience&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Road/Kill is designed to favor flow over detail, while still allowing a satisfying depth of player choice. The rules accommodate a wide variety of driving experiences, while innovative components like our Command Box, Maneuver template and Road tiles elegantly reduce clutter and keep the game moving.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A Game of Anticipation&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Road/Kill is about assessing the situation at the beginning of each turn, and who will do what. The use of four iconic dice within a snap-tite command box allows players to set their actions in secret before being revealed simultaneously with other players. In this way, surprising twists and turns are sure to happen while rewarding players with good insight.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Build&amp;rsquo;n&amp;rsquo;Battle&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Vehicles are easily designed on a template and customized to meet each player&amp;rsquo;s preference for speed, offense and defense. Once designed, vehicles are constructed with a wide variety of parts. You can be ready to play in minutes or paint your creation to perfection.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
